title: Makai Tenshi Djibril: Episode 2 (Jiburiru: Second Coming)
synopsis: Otonashi Meimi is walking alone in an empty park when the demon Rococo suddenly appears. Rococo users her Eternal Arm attack on Meimi in order to separate the power of Misty Mei from within her body.
